node.text:
This project was unique in that there are two doors, one on each side of the building. Would you appreciate a hangar designed like this?

Diamond Doors manufactures bi-fold hangar doors engineered with a 10x cable safety factor. With options like auto-lock, remote opener, insulation, pedestrian door, and windows, you can create the perfect hangar door. 

One customer says “Diamond Doors are by far the best. Very safe to operate, sturdy, well documented. Their controller (the brain of the door) is fantastic. Not only do they have a superior product, but the staff were very fast to answer my questions as well.”

 

Request a free quote at DiamondDoors.com, link in bio!
